---
title: Curried Beef and Potatoes with Spinach and Garlic-Butter Naan
description: Beef simmered in an aromatic, spicy broth with potatoes, peas and spinach is pure comfort in a bowl. Use the garlic butter naan to sop up every morsel!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/cari-de-boeuf-et-pommes-de-terre-e7775a24.jpg
